{"tid":2064383,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"張達明：希望國安法執法部門安本港法律執法。","createTime":"2020-06-14T18:18:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-14T19:40:16.000Z","uid":219007,"like":1,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"c4b6139d838e539f5eb0850438666a96bce2c65f","tid":2064383,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T18:18:07.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】港大法律學院首席講師張達明認為，內地實施的成文法與其他西方國家有別，難以直接比較。<br />\n<br />\n張達明又認為，港區國安法的問題，不只是在於兩地法制不同，而是中央是否願意完全將港區國安法交由香港法庭及執法部門，按香港法律體系及程序處理，及法例會否清晰表明會符合香港一直沿用的國際人權公約。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=394433\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D394433&d=B%2FbWfq3Pg5BEfhRE9gwZ8hPkB4X9Hpa20B1QJvXseFg%3D&h=045a7ec0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D394433&h=5ca44008\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=394433</a>"},{"pid":"8518d3ffc4c28a1c97ff0ae3589d6496338db864","tid":2064383,"uid":219007,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T18:18:44.000Z","msg":"真係多謝你嘅希望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0ea0725495ad312daace8eb4eecd1f6e1033159","tid":2064383,"uid":131084,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T18:19:29.000Z","msg":"講下講下就講到拗緊點樣執行<br />\n而唔係應唔應該過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c53dd2669ca9bfcfec085ba935b50519688bf077","tid":2064383,"uid":219007,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8518d3ffc4c28a1c97ff0ae3589d6496338db864","tid":2064383,"uid":219007,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T18:18:44.000Z","msg":"真係多謝你嘅希望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T18:20:06.000Z","msg":"Btw DLLMH <br />\n<br />\n而家好似搞到冇一個社會賢達出嚟名正言順反對立法<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/n